AB  - INTERVENTION: The PQQ supplement group:PQQ;The NMN supplement group:NMN ;The PQQ with NMN supplement group:PQQ+NMN;The placebo group:cornflour; CONDITION: Sports Nutrition PRIMARY OUTCOME: Maximal oxygen uptake;Ventilatory threshold;Creatine kinase;Tumor Necrosis Factor‐alpha;Lactate Dehydrogenase; Interleukin‐4;Interleukin‐6; C‐Reactive Protein;Superoxide Dismutase; SECONDARY OUTCOME: Muscle oxygen of vastus lateralis muscle;Interoception;Blood lactate; INCLUSION CRITERIA: 1.The inclusion criteria were as follows: (1). a Body Mass Inde X(BMI) between 18.5 and 24 kg/m^2; (2). regular exercise habits over the preceding three months, defined as engaging in physical exercise at least three times per week, with each session lasting at least 30 minutes and of moderate or higher intensity; (3). non‐consumption of coffee, tobacco products, and alcohol; (4).absence of cardiopulmonary disease; (5). absence of metabolic diseases such as endocrine, kidney, or gastrointestinal disorders; (6). absence of sports‐related injuries and movement disorders; (7). no medication use in the month prior to enrolment; and (8). no participation in any other clinical nutrition research trials.
